  <tr bgcolor="#13273C">
    <td colspan="2">Talk to Conladan Kevellian who can be found near the bank in Halas. He will tell you that he's been appointed to train all the new rogue recruits and help them craft their first suit of armor. He will then hand you an assembly kit. If you ask him about a certain piece of armor you'll be told what items to collect, and handed the appropriate pattern. Obtain one Polar Bear Skin, two Spiderling Legs, and three Bone Chips. Combine these items in the assembly kit to create the new material. Now combine this material with the appropriate pattern in a sewing kit to create the Bracer of the White Rose.</td>
